Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.39,0:00:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是一条萤 小学五年级生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.61,0:00:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个春天 转学来到了这间小小的分校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我叫一条萤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.66,0:00:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自东京
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.42,0:00:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 从东京过来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个字读萤呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么年级呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小五
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.59,0:00:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我小 比我小吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.72,0:00:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着不像小五呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在之前的学校闯祸了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.39,0:00:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是爸爸工作的缘故…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 很普通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵帕斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.69,0:01:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵… 喵…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========OP================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.82,0:01:13.37,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,このあたりイチバン見晴らしの良いあの木に登って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.54,0:01:21.04,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,あの子が笑う 無邪気に笑う 夢を見る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:45.44,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,空を泳いだ魚の向こうじっと目を凝らせば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:52.45,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,町の隅っこ色褪せてゆく日々がある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.74,0:01:56.66,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ゆびきりしたままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.70,0:01:59.62,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,サヨナラしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:08.63,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,果たされる日を待ってこの木に宿るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.55,0:02:12.72,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,何回も繰り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:16.89,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,そのたび涙する
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:20.52,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まって動き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:24.94,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,そのすべてを確かめるように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:32.99,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ほら やまびこが聞こえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.82,0:01:13.37,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,爬上这一带视野最美的那颗树
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.54,0:01:21.04,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子笑了 笑得天真无邪 她看到了梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:45.44,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,定定地盯着空中畅游的鱼儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:52.45,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,小镇每个角落里渐渐褪色的日子浮现出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.74,0:01:56.66,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,拉钩上吊百年不变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.70,0:01:59.62,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,即使分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:08.63,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,等待约定实现的心情也寄托在这颗树上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.55,0:02:12.72,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一遍一遍地重复
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:16.89,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都止不住泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.52,0:02:20.52,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,停下来又继续走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:24.94,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛是要印证这一切似的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:32.99,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,山间回音响不绝 你说是不是呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:38.50,title,NTP,0,0,0,,去\N看\N星\N星\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转学过来之后 转眼就过了几天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里和以前的学校有很多不一样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都会吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同一间教室里面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有初二的小鞠前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.01,0:02:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有初一的夏海前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:02:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有小一的莲华酱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有小鞠前辈和夏海前辈的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 萤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来玩撞尺子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撞尺子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是用尺子玩的游戏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.32,0:03:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 我完全没听说过 如果那样也没问题的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿尺子和笔过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一边玩一边说明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在小夏的家玩过 所以也来说明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对准对手的尺子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它撞出桌面就赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那萤先来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 压到上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 那样没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把对手的尺子压住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手弹三次没办法脱离的话就输了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是萤的尺子把莲酱的压住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱弹三次没办法脱离的话 莲酱就输了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.49,0:03:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(500,500)\bord9\3c&H84D052&\pos(960,684)}弹三次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:04:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(500,500)\bord9\3c&H84D052&\pos(960,684)}脱离就安全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fad(500,500)\bord9\3c&H84D052&\pos(960,684)}脱离不了就出局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样呀 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤 别这么快就以为赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有注意到这尺子是怎么放的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么放…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很普通吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是说比较窄有刻度的一面朝下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这意味着什么 现在就让你见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鲤跃龙门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥 鲤跃龙门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用笔敲击尺子较薄的地方让尺子跳起来的绝招
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是几年前影姐命名的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是绝招名字呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以脱离被压的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还可以反过来把别人压住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.09,0:04:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着该我了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样莲酱就只能用燕子翻身了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用燕子翻身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 燕子翻身是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燕子翻身是在尺子的一部分突出桌子的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用笔顶着尺子移动把对手压住的绝招
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反击成功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没打赢小小鞠呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别叫我小小鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别人都叫你小小鞠吗 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人叫前辈了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海和莲华都不把我当成前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好新鲜的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.01,0:05:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得好新鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和初中的前辈在同一间教室玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两位 很抱歉打扰到你们的快乐时光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实为了今天我已经把尺子改造过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.44,0:05:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尺子的两面已经上好蜡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样降低摩擦力之后 就能使出更高级的招式了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:06:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就能把姐姐踢出局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了呀前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不过 这么滑的话很容易会自杀 没问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就只有现在能这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么姐姐 觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好危险 从上面过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜡上太多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看我就说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上蜡就是在自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是自己偷偷改造的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤 把夏海的尺子撞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那接下来就开始我的有如破竹的进攻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲华也觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次轮到我的时候 就要把刚才燕子翻身的仇报了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 轮到我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 我的尺子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.33,0:06:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我手滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥也过来玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撞尺子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐已经输了 你可以顶她的位置中途加入哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那速度开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什… 一次攻击把三人都打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 哥哥好强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱 我们不合作的话就没法赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一次攻击就把他撞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 把哥哥的尺子撞下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空 空手夺白刃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空手夺白刃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尺子被撞出去之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰到地板之前 用笔把它弹回桌面的绝招
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是高级绝招呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说哥哥是什么时候移动过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 移到正中间确保安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易回到安全地带了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:08:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了赢哥哥 我要全部托付给小夏去赌一把了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥 你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到就能明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲤跃龙门是使出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这不是压在夏海上面了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了呀 莲酱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样带着莲酱的尺子 燕子翻身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两把尺子一起压住哥哥的尺子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么艰难才两把一起压上去的 马上就脱离了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题 这样就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才只是为了逼哥哥逃到桌子边上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里轻轻推一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不撞它下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能在这里撞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 哥哥已经准备好使出空手夺白刃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 萤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那边用力打过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的尺子 莲酱的尺子和哥哥的尺子一起撞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:09:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不那样就没办法赢哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.26,0:09:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海的尺子在哥哥的尺子上面滑出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我的尺子上蜡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后当哥哥被我那把高速飞出去的尺子吸引住的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱的尺子和哥哥的尺子一起自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就三人合力 封印住空手接白刃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合力赢过哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤 撞尺子感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:09:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.02,0:10:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我想试试一个人能达到什么程度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那再来打一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我要拿第一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息时间早就已经完了…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,(Partb)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没想到用笔和尺子就能玩得那么兴奋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有弹橡皮之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弹橡皮？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是用手指弹橡皮 把对手的橡皮撞出去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用笔和橡皮还能打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还打过高尔夫球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.73,0:10:40.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高尔夫球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是高尔夫球场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想玩一下 高尔夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下个星期一我们一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.49,0:10:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会练习的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么多没玩过的游戏好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.49,0:11:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搬家到这里之后 体验到好多的第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 下次要去看星星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个能看到很多星星的山丘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这个星期六怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,(Partb)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩奇 去散步了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖 乖 不要这么急啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那出门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 去把前辈的笔记还了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高尔夫球昨天也玩过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个天气能看到星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这条路没走过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 佩奇 走一下看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩奇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.95,0:12:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从哪条路走过来的来着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是从中间那条路来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 走错了就回头走另一边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这是刚才的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走回原位的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说走左边那条路就可以了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:13:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪 刚才过来的时候有看到河吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彻底迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\pos(534,918)\frz3.33\c&HFEFDFF&}购物商城
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.30,0:13:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么地方呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎怎怎 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不认识路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想问路也找不到人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鞠前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩奇 那是小鞠前辈的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:42.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.08,0:13:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩奇 要去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很危险的 快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩奇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佩奇
Comment: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,(Partb)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这条路一直走下去就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真心对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算是回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要去看星星 其实到时候还也行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要乱逛 早点回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是去看星星而已 很快就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小萤 你要看着小鞠 不要让她乱跑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 明明我的岁数更大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:14:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 夏海前辈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海吃完晚饭就睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲华的奶奶来了 所以她来不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是那样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成两个人了 不过那样也好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 哥哥把笔记给我了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.71,0:15:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.09,0:15:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有带手电筒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题 我带了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走这边没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天白天我迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.19,0:15:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在有我在 没问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有带钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那买些果汁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在晚上买东西 感觉就像是大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般自动贩卖机在晚上 都是虫子天堂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:15:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般都这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我要橙汁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.89,0:16:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉里面有虫子青蛙之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又湿又凉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是果汁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是果汁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果汁好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.88,0:16:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没碰到虫子太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要跟妈妈说我买果汁了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被她知道我晚上买东西吃的话肯定会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.81,0:16:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓶盖掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:16:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成路边垃圾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能花太多时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来的时候再找会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.32,0:17:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那座山丘还有很远吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经走到没有路灯的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉有点可…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…怕什么的才不会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.63,0:17:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要拿着手电筒跑开哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有手电筒也没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.02,0:17:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是怕跑开的萤不小心摔倒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个… 谢谢关心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂星座吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是猎户座吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猎户座好像是冬天的星座吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.05,0:18:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那仙女座是哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.26,0:18:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到认识的星星了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的星星连起来就是拉面座
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.48,0:18:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那那边的连起来就是素面座了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不回去的话妈妈就要生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.99,0:18:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉还没看够呢 下次再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我照着脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤 为什么把灯关了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 我没有关呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它自己关的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点开开关…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.47,0:18:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开不了 好像是电池没电了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.48,0:19:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤 萤你哭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这样就哭了可不行… 不行呀 呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 太黑了 看不到回去的路呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要看看周围的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.89,0:19:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.93,0:19:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会平安把萤送回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要走开哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前 前辈认识路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.57,0:19:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也不能一直留在这
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤 注意脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要摔倒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:19:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 好像是从这边来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我觉得好像是从这边来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周围只能看见树影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪边看起来都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.72,0:20:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果走错方向的话就更加找不到路了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛也慢慢适应了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深呼吸冷静下来的话肯定能找到路的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚 刚才那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虫子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手拿到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是瓶盖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是刚才掉的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这边这条路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 应该是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤 这边 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈 那边 能看到有光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回来了哦 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.77,0:21:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一放松下来就站不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实不用背我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.17,0:21:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.58,0:21:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是前辈帮我的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站不住这事 千万不能跟夏海说呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲华也不要说呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.76,0:21:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不要说呀 绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.51,0:21:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会当成我们两个人之间的秘密的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,(Partb)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把尺子擦得闪闪发亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害的样子 不过这有意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样绝对能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.32,0:21:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤 来玩撞尺子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.49,0:21:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.74,0:22:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我脱胎换骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:21:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.70,0:22:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天一定赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.03,0:22:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会输…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(trailer)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.67,0:23:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教我学英语
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.80,0:23:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,匹萨 匹萨 匹萨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.43,0:23:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能冲动！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.14,0:23:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不知火橘子
